 \"to\": 1145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She fell to the ground on the blue carpet in front of the golden dome of Les Invalides memorial complex in the heart of Paris before grabbing a Dutch flag to celebrate an extraordinary achievement.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0260586275051984e-31, \"text\": \"Les Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the blue carpet\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"the golden dome\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary achievement\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was not easy,\\\" said Hassan, 31.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was so hot, but I was feeling OK.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never pushed myself through to the finish line as I did today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every moment in the race I was regretting that I ran the 5,000m and 10,000m.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5,000m\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000m.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was telling myself if I had not done that, I would feel great today.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the beginning to the end, it was so hard.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step of the way.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every step\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking, 'Why did I do that?\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is wrong with me?'\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back home at Eindhoven Atletiek, an athletics club in the Netherlands, young hopefuls are put through their paces, dreaming of emulating their most famous member - double Olympic champion Sifan Hassan.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"